description:
Welcome to Oslo, Norway’s vibrant capital. Set between the Oslofjord and forested hills, the city blends medieval landmarks with striking modern design. On this tour we’ll explore Akershus Fortress, walk the length of Karl Johans gate to the Royal Palace, and stop at the Nobel Peace Center—discovering how Oslo’s past and present come together. Plenty to see, so let’s get started!

Click the *Join* button now to become a VR Gorilla YouTube member, unlocking access to the full video and our complete collection of full-length videos. https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6AXBF-78lNa3_TjAIWZWmQ/join
